patient_data.ipd_description:
Clinical studies sponsored by Boehringer Ingelheim, phase 1 to IV, interventional and non-interventional, are in scope for sharing of the raw clinical study data and clinical study documents, except for the following exclusions:
studies in products where Boehringer Ingelheim is not the licence holder;
studies regarding pharmaceutical formulations and associated analytical methods, and studies pertinent to pharmacokinetics using human biomaterials;
studies conducted in a single center or targeting rare disease (because of limitations of anonymization).
For more details refer to: http://mystudywindow.com/msw/datasharing
